  <brief_title>Restricted vs. Free Knee Range Of Motion For Primary Traumatic Patellar Dislocation</brief_title>
  <official_title>RESTRICTED VS. FREE KNEE RANGE OF MOTION FOR PRIMARY TRAUMATIC PATELLAR DISLOCATION: A PROSPECTIVE RANDOMIZED STUDY</official_title>
